<Layout>
  <div class="mb-8">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold
               leading-tight tracking-tight">
      Tell us what&rsquo;s going on.<br>
      <span class="text-primary">We&rsquo;ll check what you qualify
      for.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-base opacity-75 mt-4 max-w-xl">
      Describe your situation in your own words &mdash; no forms, no
      account. We check it against real federal program rules (SNAP,
      Medicaid/CHIP, Medicare, EITC) and hand you a plan:
      what to apply for, where, and what to have ready.
    </p>
    <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-5 text-xs" aria-label="Privacy and trust">
      <li class="badge badge-outline gap-1.5 py-3">
        <span aria-hidden="true">🔒</span> Nothing you type is stored
      </li>
      <li class="badge badge-outline gap-1.5 py-3">
        <span aria-hidden="true">💚</span> Free &mdash; not a
        government site
      </li>
      <li class="badge badge-outline gap-1.5 py-3">
        <span aria-hidden="true">🤝</span> Works alongside mutual aid
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div id="flow">
    <Form action="/screen" class="card bg-base-100 shadow-lg
                                   border border-base-300/60">
      <div class="card-body">
        <label class="font-semibold" for="narrative">
          What do you need help with?
        </label>
        <p class="text-sm opacity-70">
          For example: &ldquo;I'm in Ohio, just me and my two kids, I
          lost my job last month and we're living on about $1,400 a
          month right now.&rdquo; If a disability is part of your
          situation &mdash; physical or mental health (ADHD,
          depression, anxiety, PTSD, and others all count) &mdash;
          naming it helps us point you to the right pathway.
        </p>
        <textarea id="narrative" name="narrative" required
                  class="textarea textarea-bordered w-full min-h-32
                         focus:textarea-primary transition-colors"
                  placeholder="Tell us your situation..."></textarea>
        <div class="card-actions justify-end items-center">
          <SubmitButton />
        </div>
        <p class="spinner-block text-xs opacity-70 text-right"
           aria-live="polite">
          Checking SNAP, Medicaid, Medicare, and EITC &mdash;
          usually under a minute.
        </p>
      </div>
    </Form>
  </div>
</Layout>
